<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Day 4 — How to Access a Stronger Version</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --ink: #1a1018;
  --cream: #faf6f0;
  --accent: #c9462e;
  --accent2: #e8a030;
  --muted: #7a6e6a;
  --safe: #4a8c5c;
  --border: rgba(26,16,24,0.08);
  --ibs-i: #2d6e8e;
  --ibs-b: #c9462e;
  --ibs-s: #e8a030;
  --ibs-str: #4a8c5c;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body {
  background: var(--cream); color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7; overflow-x: hidden;
}
.slide {
  min-height: 100vh; width: 100%;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center; align-items: center;
  padding: 80px 40px 80px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
}
.slide.active { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
header {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 56px;
  background: rgba(250,246,240,0.96); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 32px; z-index: 200;
}
.logo {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
}
.day-badge {
  background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding: 5px 14px; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.nav-pills { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
.pill {
  width: 28px; height: 5px; border-radius: 3px;
  background: #d0c8c0; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.pill.active { background: var(--accent); width: 40px; }
.pill.done { background: var(--accent2); }
#prog {
  position: fixed; top: 56px; left: 0; height: 2px;
  background: var(--accent); z-index: 201; transition: width 0.4s ease;
}
.nav-arrow {
  position: fixed; bottom: 32px; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
  border: none; cursor: pointer; width: 48px; height: 48px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 18px; z-index: 200; transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.nav-arrow:hover { background: var(--accent); }
#nav-prev { left: 40px; } #nav-next { right: 40px; }
.slide-counter {
  position: fixed; bottom: 38px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted);
  z-index: 200; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}
.label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px;
}
h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 80px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 24px;
}
h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.lead { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.65; color: #3d3035; max-width: 640px; }
p.body { font-size: 15px; color: #3d3035; max-width: 640px; }
.accent-text { color: var(--accent); }
.btn {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: var(--accent); color: white;
  padding: 13px 28px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;
  cursor: pointer; border: none; margin-top: 24px;
  transition: all 0.2s; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
}
.btn:hover { background: #a8382a; transform: translateY(-1px); }

/* ─── SLIDE 1: HERO ─── */
#s1 {
  background: var(--ink);
  background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 20%, rgba(45,110,142,0.18) 0%, transparent 50%),
                    radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 80%, rgba(201,70,46,0.12) 0%, transparent 45%);
}
.day-number {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(100px, 20vw, 200px); font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); position: absolute; right: -20px;
  top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
  line-height: 1; pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
}
.theme-pill {
  display: inline-flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,110,142,0.5);
  padding: 10px 20px; margin-bottom: 32px;
  font-size: 13px; color: #b0c8d8; font-style: italic;
}

/* ─── SLIDE 2: JOURNEY MAP ─── */
#s2 { background: #f5f0ea; }
.journey-track {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
  margin-top: 40px; max-width: 860px; width: 100%;
  overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 16px;
}
.jstep {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  flex: 1; min-width: 100px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
}
.jstep.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.jnode {
  width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900;
}
.jnode.done { background: rgba(201,70,46,0.15); color: var(--accent); border: 2px solid var(--accent); }
.jnode.current { background: var(--ibs-i); color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(45,110,142,0.2); }
.jnode.upcoming { background: white; color: var(--muted); border: 2px solid #ddd; }
.jconnect { flex: 1; height: 2px; margin-top: -26px; z-index: 1; }
.jlabel {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center;
  color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.05em; max-width: 80px; line-height: 1.3;
}
.jlabel.done-label { color: rgba(201,70,46,0.6); }
.jlabel.now { color: var(--ibs-i); font-weight: 700; }

/* ─── SLIDE 3: PASSIVE vs INTENTIONAL ENTRY ─── */
#s3 { background: var(--cream); }
.entry-compare {
  display: flex; gap: 0; margin-top: 36px; max-width: 800px; width: 100%;
}
.entry-side {
  flex: 1; padding: 28px 32px;
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.6s ease;
}
.entry-side.show { opacity: 1; }
.entry-side.passive { background: #f0ece8; border-top: 3px solid #b8b0a8; }
.entry-side.intentional { background: white; border-top: 3px solid var(--ibs-i); transition-delay: 0.2s; }
.entry-tag {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.entry-side.passive .entry-tag { color: #a09890; }
.entry-side.intentional .entry-tag { color: var(--ibs-i); }
.entry-side h4 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.entry-line {
  font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); padding: 8px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26,16,24,0.06); line-height: 1.5;
}
.entry-line:last-child { border: none; }
.entry-side.intentional .entry-line { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

/* ─── SLIDE 4: WHAT IS IBS ─── */
#s4 { background: var(--ibs-i); }
.ibs-definition {
  max-width: 780px; width: 100%;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
}
.ibs-definition.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.ibs-wordmark {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px); font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.ibs-full {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.ibs-def-text {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 30px); font-weight: 700;
  color: white; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.ibs-def-text span { color: var(--accent2); font-style: italic; }
.ibs-pillars {
  display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px;
}
.ibs-pillar {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  padding: 14px 20px; flex: 1; min-width: 200px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px);
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
}
.ibs-pillar.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.ibs-pillar-title {
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.ibs-pillar p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); max-width: none; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }

/* ─── SLIDE 5: THE 4-STEP SEQUENCE (OVERVIEW) ─── */
#s5 { background: #f5f0ea; }
.seq-overview {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px; margin-top: 36px; max-width: 840px; width: 100%;
}
.seq-card {
  background: white; padding: 28px;
  border-left: 4px solid transparent;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
  cursor: pointer; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.seq-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
.seq-card.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.seq-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
.seq-card.i { border-color: var(--ibs-i); }
.seq-card.b { border-color: var(--ibs-b); }
.seq-card.s { border-color: var(--ibs-s); }
.seq-card.str { border-color: var(--ibs-str); }
.seq-letter {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 64px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px; opacity: 0.15;
  position: absolute; right: 16px; top: 12px;
}
.seq-card.i .seq-letter { color: var(--ibs-i); }
.seq-card.b .seq-letter { color: var(--ibs-b); }
.seq-card.s .seq-letter { color: var(--ibs-s); }
.seq-card.str .seq-letter { color: var(--ibs-str); }
.seq-step-label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.seq-card.i .seq-step-label { color: var(--ibs-i); }
.seq-card.b .seq-step-label { color: var(--ibs-b); }
.seq-card.s .seq-step-label { color: var(--ibs-s); }
.seq-card.str .seq-step-label { color: var(--ibs-str); }
.seq-card h4 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.seq-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); max-width: none; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
.seq-cta { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }

/* ─── SLIDES 6–9: DEEP DIVES ─── */
.deep-slide { background: var(--cream); }
#s6 { background: var(--cream); }
#s7 { background: #f5f0ea; }
#s8 { background: var(--cream); }
#s9 { background: #f5f0ea; }

.deep-header {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 780px;
}
.deep-letter-block {
  width: 72px; height: 72px; flex-shrink: 0;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 40px; font-weight: 900; color: white;
}
.deep-title-block { flex: 1; }
.deep-title-block .label { margin-bottom: 4px; }
.deep-title-block h2 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px); }
.deep-title-block p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); max-width: none; margin: 0; }

.deep-not {
  max-width: 780px; width: 100%;
  background: #f0ece8; padding: 18px 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  border-left: 3px solid #c8c0b8;
  font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6;
}
.deep-not strong { color: var(--ink); }
.deep-yes {
  max-width: 780px; width: 100%;
  background: white; padding: 18px 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.7;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.deep-question {
  max-width: 780px; width: 100%;
  padding: 22px 28px; margin-top: 12px;
}
.deep-question .q-label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.deep-question .q-text {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.35; color: white;
}
.grounding-steps {
  display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 780px;
  width: 100%; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.gs-step {
  flex: 1; min-width: 160px; padding: 18px 20px;
  background: white; border-top: 3px solid var(--ibs-s);
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px);
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
}
.gs-step.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.gs-num {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(232,160,48,0.25); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.gs-step h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.gs-step p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); max-width: none; margin: 0; }

/* ─── SLIDE 10: THE RITUAL ─── */
#s10 { background: var(--ink); }
.ritual-box {
  max-width: 760px; width: 100%; margin-top: 36px;
}
.ritual-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; padding: 18px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
}
.ritual-row.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
.ritual-row:last-child { border: none; }
.ritual-letter {
  width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: white;
}
.ritual-letter.i { background: var(--ibs-i); }
.ritual-letter.b { background: var(--ibs-b); }
.ritual-letter.s { background: var(--ibs-s); }
.ritual-letter.str { background: var(--ibs-str); }
.ritual-q {
  font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cream); flex: 1; line-height: 1.4;
}
.ritual-sub { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 3px; font-weight: 400; }
.ritual-note {
  margin-top: 28px; padding: 20px 24px;
  background: rgba(232,160,48,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,48,0.25);
  font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 760px;
}
.ritual-note strong { color: var(--accent2); }

/* ─── SLIDE 11: COMMUNITY POSTS ─── */
#s11 { background: var(--ink); }
.log-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); padding: 28px;
}
.log-header {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.log-today {
  padding: 14px 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-style: italic;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent2); line-height: 1.9;
}

/* ─── SLIDE 12: TASK ─── */
#s12 { background: var(--accent); }
#s12 h2 { color: white; }
#s12 .label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.task-box {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  padding: 32px; max-width: 700px; margin-top: 32px;
}
.task-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 16px; }
.task-list li {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
  padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  font-size: 15px; color: white;
}
.task-list li:last-child { border: none; }
.task-check {
  width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.task-check.checked { background: white; border-color: white; color: var(--accent); font-size: 13px; }
.task-min {
  margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-style: italic;
}

/* ─── SLIDE 13: CLOSE ─── */
#s13 {
  background: var(--ink);
  background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 60%, rgba(45,110,142,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%);
}
#s13 h2 { color: var(--cream); }
#s13 .body { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width: 540px; }
.close-streak {
  margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; max-width: 700px;
}
.streak-day {
  width: 48px; height: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); transition: all 0.3s;
}
.streak-day.done { background: rgba(201,70,46,0.2); border-color: rgba(201,70,46,0.3); color: rgba(201,70,46,0.7); }
.streak-day.lit { background: var(--ibs-i); border-color: var(--ibs-i); color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(45,110,142,0.4); }
.next-up {
  margin-top: 36px; padding: 20px 28px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,48,0.3);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; max-width: 600px;
}
.nxt-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.nxt-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream); }
.nxt-arrow { margin-left: auto; font-size: 24px; color: var(--accent2); cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s; }
.nxt-arrow:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }

@media(max-width:640px){
  .entry-compare { flex-direction: column; }
  .seq-overview { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .grounding-steps { flex-direction: column; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">The Unmuted Voice</div>
  <div class="nav-pills" id="pills"></div>
  <div class="day-badge">Day 4 / 30</div>
</header>
<div id="prog"></div>
<button class="nav-arrow" id="nav-prev" onclick="go(-1)">←</button>
<div class="slide-counter" id="counter">1 / 14</div>
<button class="nav-arrow" id="nav-next" onclick="go(1)">→</button>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 1: HERO -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s1" data-idx="0">
  <div class="day-number">4</div>
  <div style="max-width:860px; width:100%; position:relative; z-index:2;">
    <div class="label" style="color:#7ab8d0;">Day 4 — Activation</div>
    <div class="theme-pill">✦ You do not wait for the stronger version of you to appear. You learn how to enter it on purpose.</div>
    <h1 style="color:var(--cream);">How to Access<br><span style="color:#7ab8d0;">a Stronger<br>Version.</span></h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px; color:#b8a4a0; max-width:520px; line-height:1.65; margin-bottom:0;">Today you get your first real tool. A repeatable sequence you run before any moment that matters — starting today, for the rest of the challenge.</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="go(1)" style="background:var(--ibs-i);">Begin Day 4 →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 2: JOURNEY MAP -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s2" data-idx="1">
  <div style="max-width:900px; width:100%;">
    <div class="label">Where You Are</div>
    <h2>Awareness Is Done.<br><span style="color:var(--ibs-i);">Now We Act.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Three days of seeing the gap clearly. Today the work changes. You are no longer just identifying the pattern — you are learning to interrupt it before it starts.</p>

    <div class="journey-track" id="journeyTrack">
      <div class="jstep">
        <div class="jnode done">✓</div>
        <div class="jlabel done-label">Entry &amp;<br>Initiation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="jconnect" style="background:var(--accent);"></div>
      <div class="jstep">
        <div class="jnode done">✓</div>
        <div class="jlabel done-label">The Voice<br>Gap</div>
      </div>
      <div class="jconnect" style="background:var(--accent);"></div>
      <div class="jstep">
        <div class="jnode done">✓</div>
