      Most communication training teaches you what to say and how to say it. Identity Based Speaking works at the layer underneath that — <strong style="color:white;">the identity you are speaking from.</strong> Because the same words land completely differently depending on the version of yourself they come from. Change the identity you speak from — and everything else changes with it.
    </p>

